snippet.title: Derrick the Deathfin - Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Eat to survive in Derrick the Deathfin,an action platformer game by Different Tuna! Fast-paced Derrick the Deathfin might be the world's first papercraft-powered PSN game.

Release Date: Q3 2012
Exclusively on: PlayStation 3
Genre: Action 
Developer: Different Tuna

Learn more about Derrick at IGN:
http://ps3.ign.com/objects/129/129921.html

Subscribe to IGN's channel for reviews, guides, trailers and all things gaming: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ignentertainment
